			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Repro steps:\r\nFirst use Debug Book: Go to region > Act 1 > UND - Underdark > Fearful Rothe\r\nSeveral variations in dialogue depending on what player does from here:\r\nVariation 1: Use roll amazing. Walk towards the nearby Rothe to trigger a conversation with Skarjall.  Pick 1 > 2. Then talk to the Rothe. Pick 2 and roll the dice.\r\nVariation 2: Use roll amazing. Walk towards the nearby Rothe to trigger a conversation with Skarjall.  Pick 1 > 1 > 1, roll dice, then Pick 1. Next talk to the Rothe. Pick 2 and roll dice.\r\nVariation 3: Walk towards the nearby Rothe to trigger a conversation with Skarjall.  Pick Leave. Then Ctrl+Shift+K on the Cave-In (the rubble behind the Rothe)."
				},
